data.description: There are so many things to love about this meticulously maintained three-bedroom, two-bath home. You'll love the clean lines and modern, yet comfortable style of this home as you enter the foyer. To the left are two secondary bedrooms served by a full bath. Straight ahead is the open living room that flows into the kitchen and dining area. You'll notice the beautiful laminate flooring, and soaring ceilings. The kitchen is the crown jewel of this home with granite countertops throughout. The large island has plenty of room for eating, cooking, and visiting. The perimeter includes tons of solid-wood cabinets and counter space, a separate coffee area, and a full pantry. On the opposite side of the living room is the primary suite that encompasses a large bedroom, roomy closet, and full bath. Additional features of the home include plenty of storage, separate laundry room, and two-car garage. Out back, you'll find a large fenced yard and covered patio that's perfect for hanging out. You don't want to miss this fabulous home in an established, quiet Yukon neighborhood, conveniently located just four minutes from the Kilpatrick Turnpike, so it's close to everything! Book your exclusive tour today!
